text:
In order to make the VAJ tasks work with the latest versions of VAJ (3.5.3 & 
4.0) the following must be done:

The following lines in VAJToolsServlet

import javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet;
import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;
import javax.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;
import javax.servlet.ServletException;


must be changed to

import com.ibm.ivj.toolserver.servletclasses.servlet.http.HttpServlet;
import com.ibm.ivj.toolserver.servletclasses.servlet.http.HttpServletRequest;
import com.ibm.ivj.toolserver.servletclasses.servlet.http.HttpServletResponse;
import com.ibm.ivj.toolserver.servletclasses.servlet.ServletException;


and the instructions detailing how to export certain classes to the file 
system, must be changed to export ALL ant classes to the file system !
